Node, NPM, Bower, Grunt:
-Yeoman: yo, grunt-cli, generator angular, generator-karma


curl -sL https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_6.x | sudo -E bash -
sudo apt-get install -y nodejs

sudo apt-get install -y npm
sudo npm install -g bower
sudo npm install -g grunt-cli
sudo npm install -g bower yo generator-karma generator-angular

To use yeoman:

All of them say "Conflict package.json" with a warning, otherwise it works
Also: "Please update to minimatch 3.02"

update npm: npm install npm@latest -g

or try:

npm i -g npm-check-updates
npm-check-updates -u
npm install

http://stackoverflow.com/questions/16073603/how-do-i-update-each-dependency-in-package-json-to-the-latest-version

For quiz2 create a module, first clone:
https://github.com/udacity/FEF-Quiz-Angular-Module
Then sudo npm install, bower install
grunt serve to run